<p>Wednesday 27 June</p>
<p>Apart from Duty we get a day off whenever we like, to visit Amiens.  Parties go every day in Motor Ambulances to Albert Station thence per train to Amiens.<br/>Football matches are also regular events.  In Rugby Matches our team never meets with defeat.</p>
